I12(2) the development of better methods for predicting the power potential and longevity of geothermal reservoirs;

I12(3) the determination and assessment of the nature and power potential of the deeper unexplored parts of high temperature geothermal convection systems; and

I12(4) the survey and assessment of regional and national geothermal resources of all types.

