I89. Geothermal demonstration plants and projects

I19(a) Design and construction

I11The Chairman, acting through the appropriate Federal agencies and in cooperation with non-Federal entities, shall initiate a program to design and construct geothermal demonstration plants. The specific goals of such program shall include_

I12(1) the development of economical geothermal resources production systems and components which meet environmental standards;

I12(2) the design of plants to produce electric power and, where appropriate, the large-scale production and utilization of any useful by-products;

