I89. Objectives of fund

I19(a) Priorities

I11Expenditure of moneys from the fund on lands and water eligible pursuant to section 1234 of this title for the purposes of this subchapter, except as provided for under section 1240a of this title, shall reflect the following priorities in the order stated:

I12(1)(A) the protection;ÿ1A\1\N of public health, safety, and property from extreme danger of adverse effects of coal mining practices;

