I12(B) the restoration of land and water resources and the environment that_

I13(i) have been degraded by the adverse effects of coal mining practices; and

I13(ii) are adjacent to a site that has been or will be remediated under subparagraph (A);

Q04

I12(2)(A) the protection of public health and safety from adverse effects of coal mining practices;

I12(B) the restoration of land and water resources and the environment that_

I13(i) have been degraded by the adverse effects of coal mining practices; and

I13(ii) are adjacent to a site that has been or will be remediated under subparagraph (A); and

